<li>A more eco-friendly approach compared to proof-of-work.</li>
</ul>



<p>As you wield your influence by staking ADA, you&#8217;re participating in a system that prioritizes environmental responsibility. The proof-of-stake method isn&#8217;t just about maintaining the blockchainit&#8217;s a statement of your commitment to a greener future, leveraging a platform where power doesn&#8217;t come at the cost of the planet.</p>



